::Information::


Year: 2014
Genre: Arcade (Shoot'em up)
Developer: Dugan, Gabor, Electric Cafe
Publisher: Tikipod Ltd
Platform: PC
Language: English
Language: No
Publication Type: License
Medicine: Not required (GOG)


::Description::


Explosive side-scrolling shooter with kittens in the lead role! Game previously appeared on the PS Vita and has received good reviews from the press and critics. This action-oriented side-scrolling shooter from studios Tikipod and SCEA.


::System Requirements::


> Operating system: Windows XP (SP3), Windows Vista (SP2), Windows 7/8
> Processor: 1.2Ghz Processor
> Memory: 1 GB RAM
> Video: DirectX 9.0c-compatible graphics card with 128 MB VRAM
> Sound Card: Sound device compatible with DirectX 9.0
> Free space on hard disk: 140 MB


::Bonus Contents::

Manual
Wallpaper
Soundtrack sample (2 tracks)
Poster
Art creation booklet
6 Avatars
